{"tid":2404474,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"翠華駱克道四層巨舖傳獲茶餐廳45萬頂租　租金跌百萬","createTime":"2021-02-11T17:18:52.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-15T12:32:56.000Z","uid":36494,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6e17f8b35a117a12a8894a128ba9adbc268933c3","tid":2404474,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T17:18:52.000Z","msg":"經歷逾一年新冠肺炎疫情困擾，部分飲食業租戶開始在核心區尋找舖位。有市場消息透露，<span class=\"red\">原由翠華餐廳以146.4萬元承租的銅鑼灣駱克道485號四層共8,000平方呎巨舖，市傳新近獲另一茶餐廳以每月約45萬元頂租，跌租逾百萬元或7成。<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2014年簽下10年長租約<br />\n<br />\n上述舖位為駱克道485號地下及一至三樓，每層面積約2,000平方呎，合共8,000平方呎。翠華餐廳在2014年1月進駐上述巨舖，簽下為期10年的長租約，首5年租金122萬元，隨後5年則上升至146.4萬元。租約期至2023年12月底。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n去年2月起停業　代理料翠華已納空租一年<br />\n<br />\n不過翠華餐廳在2020年2月份起停止營運上述舖位，停業已經一年。由於翠華與該舖位業主仍有租約在身，有區內代理估計，過去停業的一年翠華餐廳仍需要每月「納空租」，即期間大概已支付了約共1,756萬元。<br />\n<br />\n而是次雖然獲得新租戶頂租，但所支付的租金僅約45萬元，估計翠華餐廳在尚餘的租約期，即2021年2月至2023年12月底，仍需要每月向業主支付原本租金的餘額，即約101.4萬元。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%9C%B0%E7%94%A2%E6%A8%93%E5%B8%82/584316/%E5%81%9C%E6%A5%AD%E4%B8%80%E5%B9%B4-%E7%BF%A0%E8%8F%AF%E9%A7%B1%E5%85%8B%E9%81%93%E5%9B%9B%E5%B1%A4%E5%B7%A8%E8%88%96%E5%82%B3%E7%8D%B2%E8%8C%B6%E9%A4%90%E5%BB%B345%E8%90%AC%E9%A0%82%E7%A7%9F-%E7%A7%9F%E9%87%91%E8%B7%8C%E7%99%BE%E8%90%AC\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%259C%25B0%25E7%2594%25A2%25E6%25A8%2593%25E5%25B8%2582%2F584316%2F%25E5%2581%259C%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%25B9%25B4-%25E7%25BF%25A0%25E8%258F%25AF%25E9%25A7%25B1%25E5%2585%258B%25E9%2581%2593%25E5%259B%259B%25E5%25B1%25A4%25E5%25B7%25A8%25E8%2588%2596%25E5%2582%25B3%25E7%258D%25B2%25E8%258C%25B6%25E9%25A4%2590%25E5%25BB%25B345%25E8%2590%25AC%25E9%25A0%2582%25E7%25A7%259F-%25E7%25A7%259F%25E9%2587%2591%25E8%25B7%258C%25E7%2599%25BE%25E8%2590%25AC&d=fMmZVRBh8JxXvfCabRklGVEyhmTkDJ%2BTCVbHNRNdZc8%3D&h=da195cce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%9C%B0%E7%94%A2%E6%A8%93%E5%B8%82/584316/%E5%81%9C%E6%A5%AD%E4%B8%80%E5%B9%B4-%E7%BF%A0%E8%8F%AF%E9%A7%B1%E5%85%8B%E9%81%93%E5%9B%9B%E5%B1%A4%E5%B7%A8%E8%88%96%E5%82%B3%E7%8D%B2%E8%8C%B6%E9%A4%90%E5%BB%B345%E8%90%AC%E9%A0%82%E7%A7%9F-%E7%A7%9F%E9%87%91%E8%B7%8C%E7%99%BE%E8%90%AC</a>"},{"pid":"84f99e9401a33ab9fc4dc13a6c41d135bc7bf8e1","tid":2404474,"uid":35296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T17:19:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0921b911da07c9c66de62bb97eb7f7d99760cb8","tid":2404474,"uid":300006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T18:19:56.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"afde96fd1c7ed7e2e668571bc1d324ccf020e690","tid":2404474,"uid":267488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T12:02:06.000Z","msg":"45萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d05bccb6893266f0e05bccd8a74fc1eb352b53d","tid":2404474,"uid":137080,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T12:04:16.000Z","msg":"其實月租百幾個真係好癲<br />\n而家反而正常番D"},{"pid":"16a2634896d566c1200f14cb51b06e37cf420a4f","tid":2404474,"uid":297997,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9d05bccb6893266f0e05bccd8a74fc1eb352b53d","tid":2404474,"uid":137080,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T12:04:16.000Z","msg":"其實月租百幾個真係好癲<br />\n而家反而正常番D"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T12:32:56.000Z","msg":"而家都唔正常<br />\n<br />\n人工低，又OT"}]}